    <h1>Privacy <em>Policy</em></h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: <b>8 July 2026</b></p>
  </div>

  <p style="color:var(--muted);margin:40px 0 0">This Privacy Policy explains how <strong style="color:var(--ink)">Games Fort Studios</strong> ("we", "us", "our") collects, uses, shares and protects information when you use our websites, games, apps and related services (together, the "Services"). By using our Services, you agree to the practices described here.</p>

  <nav class="toc" aria-label="Contents">
